    <string name="label_howto_summary">Swipe anywhere to move the paddle. Drag to aim and release to launch. Magnet powerups can catch balls for a skill shot. Collect powerups to stack abilities. Use the HUD to monitor score, lives, and timers.</string>
    <string name="label_howto_powerups_header">▼ Powerups</string>
    <string name="label_howto_powerups_list">• Multi-ball: Adds extra balls\n• Laser: Fires beams at bricks (two-finger tap or FIRE button)\n• Guardrail: Safety net below paddle\n• Shield: Absorbs a miss\n• Extra life: Gain one additional life\n• Wide paddle: Expands paddle size\n• Shrink: Temporarily reduces paddle width\n• Slow: Slows gameplay briefly\n• Overdrive: Speeds up the action\n• Fireball: Pierces through bricks\n• Magnet: Pulls powerups and catches balls on contact\n• Gravity Well: Bends ball paths toward center\n• Ball Splitter: Splits balls into more\n• Freeze: Nearly stops time for a moment\n• Pierce: Balls pass through bricks</string>
    <string name="label_howto_bricks_header">▼ Brick Types</string>
    <string name="label_howto_bricks_list">• Standard: one hit\n• Reinforced: two hits\n• Armored: three hits\n• Explosive: damages surrounding bricks\n• Unbreakable: requires fireball/laser\n• Moving: slides horizontally\n• Spawning: breaks into child bricks\n• Phase: changes phases with new HP\n• Boss: multi-phase heavyweight brick</string>
    <string name="label_howto_modes_header">▼ Game Modes</string>
    <string name="label_howto_modes_list">Classic: Standard breakout progression.\nTimed Challenge: Score high in 2:30.\nEndless: Infinite levels with scaling difficulty.\nGod Mode: Practice without losing lives.\nLevel Rush: Beat each stage before time expires.\nVolley: Launch a chain, then survive descending rows.\nTunnel Siege: Break through a fortress ring via a narrow entry lane.\nSurvival: One life with faster speed ramps.\nInvaders: Bounce shots to clear ships while dodging fire.</string>
